Location: Lillydale Rd & Queelup Rd, North Boyanup

Description: Cyclists almost hit, cars having to move right over to travel to avoid large trucks, cars going too fast and poor visibility at sunset and during night. Very dangerous stretch of road that has seen increased traffic over last 5-10 years.

Location: Lillydale Rd & South Western Hwy, North Boyanup
Description: Many vehicles entering South Western Hwy from Lillydale Road do not stop and wait until it's safe to enter a busy 110km/h speed zone. This causes dangerous situations
